# Google OAuth2 credentials for Drive sync
# Create at: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
#   → Application type: "Desktop app" (public client, no secret needed, works with PKCE)
# Enable: Google Drive API, scope: https://www.googleapis.com/auth/drive.appdata
# Add redirect URI: http://localhost:5174/oauth-callback and your production URL
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
